        Constructor for merchant information, specifying also the flag if SDK is pointing to TEST environment and if the CVC field will be shown or not

        Important: Note that disabling Security Code entry by setting _cvcRequired=False_ is submitted to both approval from your acquirer and activation by Netaxept customer service. Before proceeding, please contact your Netaxept customer service.

        Parameters:
        merchantId - Merchant id
        testMode - Flag to specify if test environment should be used
        cvcRequired - Flag to specify if CVC/CVV field will be required
